  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13102828/sustainability-hero-900.jpg" alt="SustainabilityHero" data-udi="umb://media/20975f889216458aa637fb6924ff9291" /></p>
<strong>Our Sustainability Journey -</strong>Our employees and customers love the great outdoors. The places we visit are special, and it’s our responsibility to keep them that way, long into the future. As part of Hotelplan UK, Inghams and Santa’s Lapland were early signatories of the Glasgow Declaration on Climate Action in Tourism, to halve emissions by 2030 and reach net zero by 2050. We’ve also signed the WTTC’s Nature Positive Travel and Tourism commitment.<strong><br /></strong></div>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"></div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Protecting our futures</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Our Wheel of Impact guides us on the priority areas we can influence for good, under our three main pillars of action: climate, biodiversity and community.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 500px;" src="/media/13102832/wheel-of-impact-v6-700x700.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500" alt="WheelofImpact700x700" data-udi="umb://media/f53a7c6174864f99a1acfe68f242d151" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Climate</h2>
<p>Goal: 50% reduction in our greenhouse gas intensity by 2030.​</p>
<p>Read more about our carbon measurement and our investment in carbon removal projects below.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 250px; height: 250px;" src="/media/13102829/transport-with-a-ticket-250x250.jpg?width=250&amp;height=250" alt="TransportTicket" data-udi="umb://media/f5593cf51b5b46ff9a839bab94060d21" /><br />
<p style="text-align: center;">Transport - Offering lower carbon <em><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5}" title="Ski holidays by train">transport choices</a></strong></em> where possible, such as holidays by train.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100624/accommodation-250x250-v2.jpg" alt="accommodationicon" data-udi="umb://media/9e7446f042cf414f9812f178de7544ca" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Accommodation - Working with partners to measure, report and reduce their footprint.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100617/activities-250x250.jpg" alt="activityicon" data-udi="umb://media/2b7a4189e80f456693ac2522395390f4" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span></span>Activities - Exploring <strong><em><a data-udi="umb://document/f3dbae7291f94e189e126ec859efa344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f3dbae7291f94e189e126ec859efa344}" title="Walking Holidays">lower impact</a></em></strong>, nature-friendly activities.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Biodiversity</h2>
<p>Positively contribute to regenerating and protecting 30% of land and water for biodiversity by 2030 AND reduce our use of natural resources​.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100622/purchasing-250x250.jpg" alt="purchasingicon" data-udi="umb://media/2e8f4a403baa40158b5cec9b8452dfe5" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Ethical purchasing -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Prioritising seeking <em><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ea4d933f6e4e4c189eb995e7bf4f1bd4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ea4d933f6e4e4c189eb995e7bf4f1bd4}" title="Insider's Guide: EcoSki - Interview with founder Rachael">nature-friendly</a></strong></em> suppliers; reusing and repurposing.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100620/food-250x250.jpg" alt="foodicon" data-udi="umb://media/1ca082bf72344467a4b45a534b647199" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Celebrating Food &amp; Drink -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">More plant-based ingredients and less food miles. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100621/protection-250x250.jpg" alt="protectingicon" data-udi="umb://media/91fac38a338b40138f1e9688747e98f0" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Protection and restoration -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Protecting <em><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/58360366a5274b68b2a6a53bba22ec4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58360366a5274b68b2a6a53bba22ec4d}" title="Our Animal Protection Policy">nature and animals</a></strong></em> and regenerating biodiversity.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Community</h2>
<p>Engaging and empowering communities</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100618/charity-250x250.jpg" alt="charityicon" data-udi="umb://media/64bf1bc22ebc4ee6be29e9f659e9b7cb" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/791fa5aa176246cbbaa02331f3c763ef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/791fa5aa176246cbbaa02331f3c763ef}" title="Partnerships"><em><strong>Charity partnerships &amp; Volunteering</strong></em></a> - Working with charities and volunteering to make a difference on key issues.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100619/conversation-250x250.jpg" alt="customericon" data-udi="umb://media/573c27c9cf754f55ba5a62e700ac9582" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Customer conversation - Inspiring customers to travel more <strong><em><a data-udi="umb://document/70b350895a5d4ceeaa62215a223e24b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70b350895a5d4ceeaa62215a223e24b5}" title="Responsible Walking">sustainably and responsibly</a></em></strong>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100615/accessibility-250x250.jpg" alt="inclusionicon" data-udi="umb://media/a2b6efc18cee40538617ea2de7d19aad" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span></span><em><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/db4567ae70304c2892abca6e930c2def" href="/{localLink:umb://document/db4567ae70304c2892abca6e930c2def}" title="Snow Camp">Inclusion for all</a></strong></em> - Bettering our holidays so they are fair and just for everyone.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><iframe width="100%" height="400" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9wR_YGu169c" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Climate Action Plan</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">We published our climate and biodiversity papers in 2023 which directly addresses our impact and what we are doing to reduce and mitigate it.</p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Impact reports</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">In December 2023, we published the results of our second carbon audit and shared how we’re progressing towards our goals</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/b3e8c2d9ef9643828be3c9a2668aa603" href="/media/13098529/biodiversity-paper-2023.pdf" title="Biodiversity Paper 2023"><img src="/media/13094827/acob023_hotelplan_sustainability-report_biodiversity-paper_01.jpg" alt="Biodiversity 2023" data-udi="umb://media/4b306a37b69d42559c38103fa14648e5" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/2be48a811a914d2aab475e7ddb2525b0" href="/media/13098530/climate-paper-2023.pdf" title="Climate Paper 2023"><img src="/media/13094828/acob023_hotelplan_sustainability-report_climate-paper_01.jpg" alt="Climate Paper 2023" data-udi="umb://media/c19ee5a404a84c7aa51efdca4f41df03" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/441c36f2620b4ced8bfb4dbfe89e93d1" href="/media/13102309/202312-final-hotelplan-uk-protecting-our-futures-planet-and-people-report.pdf" title="Hotelplan UK Protecting Our Futures Planet And People Report"><img src="/media/13102308/hotelplan-uk-protecting-our-futures-front-cover.jpg" alt="People&amp;Planet" data-udi="umb://media/f9b9d0077af34955a23a1973a498b7fe" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: left;">Please contact us on sustainability@hotelplan.co.uk with any feedback or questions you may have regardsing our sustainability journey.</p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
